Hellooo  family!!❤🇮🇳

I take the privilege informing all of you that "I have successfully made it to the peak of Mt. Annapurna, (8091 mtrs) 10th highest mountain in the world on 16th April 2021 at 1.30pm.
And also I am the first Indian woman to scale Mt.Annapurna 1.

I am safe and sounding because of your prayers, support and love. 

Thank yoo so much @lakpasherpa1991 @mingdorchi @pioneer_expeditions and great team Pioneer.

latestPosts.caption:
A dream come true.. 

13th November 2021, a day to remember. 

I was equally excited and nervous to receive the Tenzing Norgey National Adventure Award  by the honorable president of India, Shri Ramnath kovind at Rastrapathi bhavan in the presence of various diplomats of the our country.

Heart felt gratitude to the committee for recognizing me and putting my name first among the category. 

Parents,Guru, Sherpa's,friends, family, all those who blessed and kept me in your prayers, my deepest thank you.. 

I also congratulate my fellow recipients for the award. 
Jai Hind 🇮🇳

#tenzingnorgaynationaladventureaward
#India
#priyankamohite
